== Russian ==
=== Word-formation ===
''prefix'' [[胁芯褋-]] + ''root'' [[褋谢邪胁邪|褋谢邪胁]] + [[-谢-]] + [[-褟-]] + [[-褌褜]] (see)

=== Verb ===
'''胁芯褋褋谢邪胁谢褟虂褌褜''' (vosslavl'谩t') ''(transitive, imperfective)''

# ''(poetic)'' to [[praise]], to [[glorify]], to [[make famous]] (''to give praise or glory to smb.'')

